Authorities are now questioning
the faculty and staff members of

00:03:31.461 --> 00:03:33.839
the private middle school.
As well as, focusing their

00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:36.383
investigation on previous
interactions the victims

00:03:36.425 --> 00:03:38.385
might have had with one another.

00:03:45.434 --> 00:03:48.061
[YUUYA] Is this that crazy
"spiritual healing" stuff?

00:03:48.103 --> 00:03:50.981
Yeah. But after seeing demons
and all that other crazy shit,

00:03:51.022 --> 00:03:54.109
we should be the last
people to doubt her powers.

