It appears that your friend has
had her consciousness imprisoned

00:04:01.450 --> 00:04:05.454
in someone else's mindscape.
Someone with considerable power.

00:04:05.495 --> 00:04:06.788
Mindscape?

00:04:06.830 --> 00:04:08.749
[IWAYAMA]
Very powerful mental powers.

00:04:08.790 --> 00:04:10.333
This person seems
to have an extremely

00:04:10.375 --> 00:04:12.586
strong hold on your friend.

00:04:12.627 --> 00:04:14.337
[KYOICHI] That sure doesn't
sound like you're average person

00:04:14.379 --> 00:04:16.298
off the streets, huh?

00:04:16.339 --> 00:04:18.175
[YUUYA]
Which means...

00:04:19.050 --> 00:04:20.886
[TATSUMA]
It's someone who has the Power.

00:04:22.345 --> 00:04:23.930
Who the hell would do this?

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:27.601
[IWAYAMA] In any case, if she
remains in this comatose state,

00:04:27.642 --> 00:04:29.728
her body will break down and
she will die.

00:04:29.770 --> 00:04:31.438
Her life is in danger.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:34.733
Come on, you can do something,
can't you?! I mean, I believe

00:04:34.775 --> 00:04:38.528
that's why we came to this
freakshow of a hospital!

00:04:38.570 --> 00:04:41.698
[IWAYAMA] Well! Seems you've
learned to use that mouth

00:04:41.740 --> 00:04:44.409
of yours quite well.
I remember a certain little

00:04:44.451 --> 00:04:47.829
brat, who used to come to
me whining and crying.

00:04:47.871 --> 00:04:50.707
No need to bring up
stupid stuff from the past!

00:04:50.749 --> 00:04:53.335
[IWAYAMA] Alright, settle down,
the important thing right now is

00:04:53.376 --> 00:04:56.755
for you to find out how to save
your friend, is that right?

00:04:56.797 --> 00:04:58.673
Unfortunately, all
we can do right now

00:04:58.715 --> 00:05:00.842
is provide
emergency treatment.

00:05:00.884 --> 00:05:02.552
So, what do you mean?

00:05:02.594 --> 00:05:04.888
The only thing I can do is to
attempt to stop the other

00:05:04.930 --> 00:05:08.183
person's thoughts from fully
imprisoning her consciousness.

00:05:08.225 --> 00:05:10.268
[IWAYAMA] To save her,
you'll have to find whoever

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:14.105
is behind this and stop
that person yourselves.

00:05:14.147 --> 00:05:16.441
And you'll want to do that
as quickly as possible.

00:05:16.483 --> 00:05:19.611
What if this person
really does have the Power?

00:05:19.986 --> 00:05:21.613
We have to
stop whoever this is,

00:05:21.655 --> 00:05:23.156
even if it means
we have to kill 'em.

