[MAIKO]
Look! A doggie...

00:06:21.381 --> 00:06:23.466
It was just there in front of
the hospital.

00:06:23.508 --> 00:06:24.718
[KYOICHI]
Huh? A dog?

00:06:24.759 --> 00:06:26.678
[IWAYAMA]
Oh, don't mind her.

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:29.973
Maiko sees all sorts of
spirits and other things.

00:06:30.015 --> 00:06:32.309
Do you mean,
like, ghosts and stuff?

00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:34.728
[MAIKO]
Mmmhmm.

00:06:39.733 --> 00:06:43.653
I sense that he really wants to
see her pretty badly.

00:06:45.906 --> 00:06:48.575
[ANKO]
Hmmm...

00:06:48.617 --> 00:06:51.870
In the city... a baffling string
of unexplained comas...

00:06:51.912 --> 00:06:54.456
Students of the same
private middle school...

00:06:59.753 --> 00:07:02.422
[screams]

00:07:12.724 --> 00:07:14.142
[ANKO]
Here it is.

00:07:14.184 --> 00:07:16.311
[phone ringing]

00:07:16.353 --> 00:07:18.563
[ANKO] Hello, I'm with
the Kagura Middle School

00:07:18.605 --> 00:07:19.856
Alumni Association.

00:07:19.898 --> 00:07:22.442
In fact, I'm a
graduate of Kagura myself...

00:07:22.484 --> 00:07:24.736
I was hoping to ask you a
couple of questions about our

00:07:24.778 --> 00:07:26.154
old middle school days.

00:07:26.196 --> 00:07:27.489
[ANKO'S MOM] Kyoko!
Where do you think you're

00:07:27.530 --> 00:07:28.990
going at this hour
of the night?!

00:07:29.032 --> 00:07:30.784
[ANKO] I'm going
out for a walk, Mom!

00:07:30.825 --> 00:07:33.036
[phone ringing]

00:07:36.456 --> 00:07:39.417
[KOMAKI] Anko?
Aoi's is still unconscious.

00:07:39.459 --> 00:07:41.753
We're at the hospital right now.

00:07:41.795 --> 00:07:44.464
Huh? What?

00:07:47.592 --> 00:07:49.803
[YUUYA] So... Anko said
to meet her in Tsukimidai

00:07:49.844 --> 00:07:51.221
as soon as possible.

00:07:51.262 --> 00:07:52.764
[KOMAKI] She didn't tell
me any details, but she said

00:07:52.806 --> 00:07:55.976
it's got something to do with
what's going on with Aoi.

00:07:57.185 --> 00:07:59.312
I want to find
out what's going on.

00:07:59.354 --> 00:08:00.772
[KYOICHI] No worries!
Princess will be fine as long

00:08:00.814 --> 00:08:03.358
as The Old Lady
watching over her!

00:08:13.702 --> 00:08:15.954
[IWAYAMA] We must make sure
this holds until they find

00:08:15.996 --> 00:08:18.623
the location
of the spell caster.

00:08:18.665 --> 00:08:20.291
[MAIKO]
Right!

00:08:24.254 --> 00:08:26.840
This is the guy! This is
the guy who's responsible

00:08:26.881 --> 00:08:29.300
for putting Aoi in a coma!

00:08:30.635 --> 00:08:32.095
Uh... Who's he?

00:08:32.137 --> 00:08:34.931
[ANKO] Reiji Sagaya. He's the
one who's behind all those

00:08:34.973 --> 00:08:37.434
high school students
falling into comas!

00:08:37.475 --> 00:08:39.686
[YUUYA] H-How do
you know all this?!

00:08:39.728 --> 00:08:42.397
[condescending laugh]

00:08:43.857 --> 00:08:50.822
[ANKO] I am the soon-to-be
journalist phenom... Kyoko Tono.

00:08:50.864 --> 00:08:54.868
When it comes to
students in the Tokyo area,

00:08:54.909 --> 00:08:58.955
I know all about them!
I know their test scores,

00:08:58.997 --> 00:09:00.999
I know everything
from what's in your lunch,

00:09:01.041 --> 00:09:02.709
right down to the
holes in your socks!

00:09:02.751 --> 00:09:05.086
What?...Really?! Wow.

00:09:10.717 --> 00:09:13.094
[ANKO] All of the students
who've fallen into comas

00:09:13.136 --> 00:09:15.930
were bullies from Kagura
Middle School.

00:09:15.972 --> 00:09:19.184
And their main target of their
bullying was Reiji Sagaya.

00:09:19.225 --> 00:09:21.561
Rumor has it that they were
pretty mean and ruthless

00:09:21.603 --> 00:09:25.899
with him. It's surprising that
none of this was discovered.

00:09:28.735 --> 00:09:30.236
[groans]

00:09:45.919 --> 00:09:47.587
[blow lands]

00:09:53.176 --> 00:09:55.929
[muffled grunting]

00:10:03.061 --> 00:10:07.565
[muffled screaming]

00:10:12.779 --> 00:10:14.656
[ANKO] Sagaya hasn't set
foot outside his house

00:10:14.697 --> 00:10:16.199
since middle school.

00:10:16.241 --> 00:10:19.536
But, since last spring,
rumor has been going around,

00:10:19.577 --> 00:10:21.996
among the guys who
used to bully Sagaya,

00:10:22.038 --> 00:10:23.289
that he's going
to come after each and

00:10:23.331 --> 00:10:26.626
every one of them and get
even... in their dreams!

00:10:26.668 --> 00:10:28.545
His parents even treat
him like some kind of monster

00:10:28.586 --> 00:10:30.839
or something.

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:32.632
[KYOICHI]
This past spring?

00:10:32.674 --> 00:10:34.342
In their dreams, huh?

00:10:34.384 --> 00:10:37.720
If he really is another person
with this Power we all have what

00:10:37.762 --> 00:10:40.014
you're saying can really happen.

00:10:40.056 --> 00:10:42.725
But why is he after Aoi?
Why is he involving Aoi

00:10:42.767 --> 00:10:45.103
and making her go
through all this?

00:10:45.145 --> 00:10:48.523
[ANKO] I don't know...
But, Aoi also went to

00:10:48.565 --> 00:10:50.316
Ka-gu-ra Middle School!

00:10:50.358 --> 00:10:52.735
There's gotta be
some kind of connection.

00:10:52.777 --> 00:10:54.737
[KYOICHI] Okay, then we have
to find out where he lives!

00:10:54.779 --> 00:10:56.531
[ANKO]
Hold one second!

00:10:56.573 --> 00:10:58.992
Why do you think
I've called you all here?

00:10:59.033 --> 00:11:04.789
This is where he
lives! Unit #504.

00:11:04.831 --> 00:11:05.832
Thank you, Anko.

00:11:05.874 --> 00:11:07.458
Alright, let's do it!

00:11:12.255 --> 00:11:14.257
[KOMAKI]
Kyoko...

00:11:14.299 --> 00:11:15.717
I'm sorry.

00:11:17.135 --> 00:11:18.553
I thought you...

00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:22.849
No need to say it, I know!
Even if it would be the scoop

00:11:22.891 --> 00:11:24.976
of the century,
your secret's safe with me,

00:11:25.018 --> 00:11:27.937
so don't worry, okay!

00:11:28.313 --> 00:11:29.689
[KOMAKI]
Huh?

00:11:30.690 --> 00:11:32.984
A secret team of
justice fighters battling

00:11:33.026 --> 00:11:35.111
the forces of evil,
now that's hot!

00:11:35.153 --> 00:11:36.779
Do you think I'd let
anyone else in on that?

00:11:36.821 --> 00:11:38.698
From now on,
I'm going to devote my time

00:11:38.740 --> 00:11:40.575
to covering your story.

00:11:40.617 --> 00:11:43.536
Don't worry! No one will know
it's you guys! But in return,

00:11:43.578 --> 00:11:47.749
I get exclusive rights on the
story. You see, Komaki,

00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:52.587
I do remember how all of you
guys saved me that night.

00:11:55.006 --> 00:11:58.635
When Aoi regains consciousness,
tell her I'm sorry, okay?

00:11:58.676 --> 00:12:01.304
It's not that I was afraid of
you guys. I was just a little

00:12:01.346 --> 00:12:03.723
thrown off
guard, that's all.

00:12:03.765 --> 00:12:06.184
[ANKO]
Tell her I said sorry.

00:12:06.226 --> 00:12:08.811
If that's how you feel,
why not tell her yourself?

00:12:08.853 --> 00:12:11.689
We're going to
protect Aoi no matter what!

00:12:13.858 --> 00:12:16.486
Keep an eye on her
while we're gone, okay?

00:12:19.572 --> 00:12:20.865
Leave it to me!

00:12:28.373 --> 00:12:31.125
There was no reason.
They simply enjoyed watching

00:12:31.167 --> 00:12:37.632
me suffer over and over.
I was a toy to them.

00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:45.348
[SAGAYA] But then you,
you appeared one day.

00:13:01.072 --> 00:13:02.615
[SAGAYA]
Please stop!

00:13:02.865 --> 00:13:04.575
[BULLY] I hear that you
and Aoi Misato have been

00:13:04.617 --> 00:13:06.703
feeding this mutt.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:10.748
Yeah, who do you think you are
hanging around girls?

00:13:11.291 --> 00:13:12.959
[SAGAYA]
No! Don't!

00:13:13.376 --> 00:13:16.421
No! Don't!

00:13:16.921 --> 00:13:18.506
[SAGAYA] It's been
three years since then

00:13:18.548 --> 00:13:20.216
and not a single day went by

00:13:20.258 --> 00:13:25.930
when I didn't think of them.
Then one day, I got my chance.

00:13:25.972 --> 00:13:29.267
[strained groaning]

00:13:30.643 --> 00:13:33.730
You were the only
one who was different.

00:13:33.771 --> 00:13:36.524
Aoi, I will
always protect you.

00:13:37.525 --> 00:13:40.611
Let's stay here
together in this world.

00:13:54.542 --> 00:14:00.298
Aoi... Why won't you
please open your eyes?

00:14:04.218 --> 00:14:08.431
I get it. There's someone
holding you to that other world,

00:14:08.473 --> 00:14:09.974
isn't there?

00:14:12.143 --> 00:14:13.978
[SAGAYA]
Let's go, Tiny.

00:14:21.069 --> 00:14:28.034
Oh, come on.
It was just getting good.

00:14:41.631 --> 00:14:44.342
[KISARAGI] Just as I thought,
all the seals have been broken.

00:14:51.391 --> 00:14:55.937
[EVIL MALE MASK] You...
are a Kisaragi descendent?

00:14:57.647 --> 00:15:00.233
[IWAYAMA] O-in-shi-chi-ri
kya-ra-ro ha-u-un-ken so-wa-ka,

00:15:00.274 --> 00:15:01.692
O-in-shi-chi-ri kya-ra-ro
ha-u-un-ken so-wa-ka,

00:15:01.734 --> 00:15:06.030
--Aoi... please hang on!
--ha-u-un-ken so-wa-ka.

00:15:13.246 --> 00:15:15.206
