and getting in the perimeter

00:15:15.248 --> 00:15:16.791
is quite impressive.

00:15:16.833 --> 00:15:20.294
The doggie looks a little
different from earlier.

00:15:24.340 --> 00:15:28.928
I won't hold back on anyone who
tries to take Aoi away from me.

00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.847
A vengeful spirit?

00:15:30.888 --> 00:15:33.182
What powerful hatred.

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:42.191
[TATSIMA]
It's okay, he's alive.

00:15:42.233 --> 00:15:43.568
[KOMAKI]
This woman is okay, too.

00:15:43.609 --> 00:15:46.279
It's as if they're sleeping.

00:15:46.320 --> 00:15:48.865
[KYOICHI] I've got
a bad feeling about this.

00:15:48.906 --> 00:15:50.950
[YUUYA]
He might be in there?

00:15:52.535 --> 00:15:54.287
[TATSUMA]
What's that?

00:16:02.086 --> 00:16:04.881
[SAGAYA]
Someone's getting too nosey.

00:16:04.922 --> 00:16:07.592
Tiny, you take care of this.

00:16:07.633 --> 00:16:11.804
It appears that our young
friends have located the body.

00:16:13.848 --> 00:16:16.851
[SAGAYA]
Welcome to My Dream World.

00:16:24.317 --> 00:16:25.776
[KOMAKI]
Aoi!

00:16:26.652 --> 00:16:27.653
Let go!

00:16:27.945 --> 00:16:29.238
Aoi!

00:16:29.280 --> 00:16:30.823
[KOMAKI]
Aoi!

00:16:31.157 --> 00:16:34.118
[SAGAYA] I'm sorry, but Aoi is
mine. I won't hand her over

00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:36.078
to just anyone.

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:37.747
You bastard!

00:16:37.788 --> 00:16:40.291
Newsflash, asshole
she doesn't belong to you.

00:16:40.333 --> 00:16:42.919
So get your hands
off her, freak!

00:16:44.545 --> 00:16:47.840
You have no idea what you've
got yourselves into, do you?

00:16:47.882 --> 00:16:51.260
[SAGAYA] If you die in this
world you die in the real world.

00:16:51.302 --> 00:16:53.721
And the four of you will die.

00:16:53.763 --> 00:16:56.682
[reverberating footsteps]

00:16:58.559 --> 00:17:00.061
[KYOICHI]
Wh-What in the hell?

00:17:04.565 --> 00:17:06.108
[all scream]

00:17:09.153 --> 00:17:11.906
[IWAYAMA] Oinshichiri
kyararo hauunken sowaka,

00:17:11.948 --> 00:17:13.616
Oinshichiri kyara...

00:17:13.658 --> 00:17:15.076
[ANKO]
Aoi!

00:17:15.993 --> 00:17:18.496
[Inwayama screams]

00:17:22.375 --> 00:17:24.418
[ANKO] Let me tell you
something about journalists:

00:17:24.460 --> 00:17:26.671
We'll risk our lives anytime.

00:17:28.673 --> 00:17:31.467
and I'll never give
Aoi over to you!

00:17:37.139 --> 00:17:39.600
Daigo, Sakurai...
you guys alright?

00:17:39.642 --> 00:17:42.311
[YUUYA]
Yeah! We're okay!

00:17:49.402 --> 00:17:53.197
Hey guys! This is just a dream!
Focus your minds!

00:17:57.326 --> 00:18:00.329
N-No way! This is my dream!

00:18:00.371 --> 00:18:03.332
[KYOICHI] Too bad for you,
we're pretty "strong minded."

00:18:04.709 --> 00:18:07.712
So we're not gonna fall
for your little freak show.

00:18:09.338 --> 00:18:11.215
[IWAYAMA]
Takamizawa!

00:18:21.142 --> 00:18:23.686
[MAIKO]
Please... stop this!

00:18:36.782 --> 00:18:41.245
You were very sad, weren't
you? And full of so much pain.

00:19:07.855 --> 00:19:10.608
Fu-ru-be, yu-ra-yu-ra...

00:19:19.575 --> 00:19:21.786
You're free now.
You mustn't let the hatred

00:19:21.827 --> 00:19:23.621
within you hold you forever.

00:19:23.663 --> 00:19:27.249
Understand?
Now return to your true self.

00:19:27.291 --> 00:19:30.419
[MAIKO] Go and save the
people who are dear to you.

00:19:30.878 --> 00:19:32.922
[IWAYAMA] Release this
departed soul, begone.

00:19:32.963 --> 00:19:35.341
Release this
departed soul, begone.

