Release this
departed soul, begone. Now.

00:19:58.948 --> 00:20:02.743
If they keep coming back like
this, this will take forever!

00:20:08.207 --> 00:20:09.208
[KYOICHI]
Tatsuma!

00:20:20.511 --> 00:20:21.679
--Tatsuma!
--Hiyuu!

00:20:33.441 --> 00:20:35.025
[KYOICHI]
Tatsuma! Get him!

00:20:35.651 --> 00:20:36.777
Kyoichi...

00:20:47.371 --> 00:20:52.793
Tiny? Why did you
come back? What about Aoi?

00:20:52.835 --> 00:20:55.421
Why didn't you
bring Aoi with you?!

00:20:55.463 --> 00:20:59.675
[dog whining]

00:21:08.392 --> 00:21:10.978
[AOI]
Reiji, please stop this.

00:21:13.355 --> 00:21:16.442
Doing this won't
save you or Tiny.

00:21:16.484 --> 00:21:17.401
Aoi!

00:21:20.237 --> 00:21:22.823
[AOI] This isn't
really what you want.

00:21:22.865 --> 00:21:26.035
You should know
better than anyone.

00:21:28.204 --> 00:21:30.998
I don't want anyone, especially
a friend to go through such

00:21:31.040 --> 00:21:35.044
sorrow ever again! I can't
forgive people who harm others

00:21:35.085 --> 00:21:37.713
just for amusement,
or who would take the life

00:21:37.755 --> 00:21:40.424
of an innocent, little creature.

00:21:41.342 --> 00:21:45.721
Be strong and courageous.
Put aside your hatred!

00:21:45.763 --> 00:21:47.473
Be better than they were.

00:21:51.685 --> 00:21:58.108
No. I... I don't care what
happens to me! But I at least...

00:21:58.150 --> 00:22:01.111
I wanted to protect
Tiny at the very least!

00:22:03.155 --> 00:22:06.575
[SAGAYA] Tiny! I'm sorry
I couldn't protect you.

00:22:06.617 --> 00:22:08.327
I'm so... sorry.

00:22:11.121 --> 00:22:16.335
I wanted to be strong... enough
to protect the ones I care for.

00:22:16.377 --> 00:22:18.170
I wanted to be strong!

00:22:19.255 --> 00:22:22.341
[AOI] You can change.
I know you can.

00:22:22.383 --> 00:22:25.970
Use this power to
protect people instead.

00:22:31.809 --> 00:22:34.228
[KYOICHI]
Great, what now?!

00:22:35.563 --> 00:22:38.649
[TATSUMA]
Your dream world is collapsing.

00:22:40.609 --> 00:22:44.113
[SAGAYA]
Thank you... Aoi...

00:22:49.118 --> 00:22:51.537
[REPORTER] A follow-up story,
the high school students who had

00:22:51.579 --> 00:22:55.165
unexplainably fallen into
comatose states five days ago

00:22:55.207 --> 00:22:57.585
have all made a
full recovery as of...

00:22:57.626 --> 00:22:59.753
[IWAYAMA] They seem
to be doing just fine.

00:22:59.795 --> 00:23:03.591
We'll take care
of him here for a bit.

00:23:03.632 --> 00:23:05.759
[KYOICHI] Look at him with that
peaceful smile on his face...

00:23:05.801 --> 00:23:08.596
It seems like
his soul is saved now.

00:23:14.476 --> 00:23:18.647
[ANKO] Aoi!
Oh, thank goodness!

00:23:32.703 --> 00:23:36.373
The "Dream Master"...
What a joke.

00:23:36.415 --> 00:23:39.209
None of these
"people" are of any use!

00:23:39.251 --> 00:23:43.005
Well... now getting back
to my brave little friend.

00:23:44.214 --> 00:23:47.760
[KISARAGI]
So I was right... It is them.

00:23:56.560 --> 00:23:57.978
[TENDO]
I'm sorry to say this concludes

00:23:58.020 --> 00:24:00.314
our business for today.

00:24:00.356 --> 00:24:02.483
Until next time.

